name: THE BEAUTY EATER
description:
Episode 1 of the series "feel my pain"

Beauty standards do not need to exist.
Everyone has advantages.
Everyone has flaws.
Everyone has a uniqueness that no one else has.
Trying to live up to beauty standards will kill you.
Make yourself up to the standards of others.
This system caused many problems among us ranging from social class, economy, to racism.
If we are all the same, then who is special?
Aren't you tired of all this?
Don't mind it all.
Set your standards.
Everyone has the right to feel beautiful.
Because every human being is a beautiful creature.
